channeldata.description: This package is a generic way to obtain binutils for your system that conda-forge used to compile its ecosystem.  This compiler is, therefore, guaranteed to be ABI compatible with the conda packages you have installed.  This compiler metapackage is a convenience ONLY for users. Do NOT use this package as a build or host dependency in other recipes.
channeldata.summary: A set of programming tools for creating and managing binary programs, object files, libraries, profile data, and assembly source code.
